      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S in impeccable condition. This 996.2 iteration is powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L M96/03 flat-six engine, featuring VarioCam Plus intake-valve timing and lift for a seamless power band. The drivetrain utilizes a robust G96/01 6-speed manual transaxle delivering power to a sophisticated all-wheel-drive system with a viscous clutch center differential. The wide-body chassis remains structurally rigid, supported by a factory-tuned multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts. Deceleration is handled by 4-piston monoblock aluminum calipers over cross-drilled, ventilated rotors. This specimen displays zero cosmetic degradation, with a flawless finish and a cabin devoid of the typical bolster wear or soft-touch plastic delamination. Full service history confirms the IMS bearing and rear main seal have been addressed, ensuring mechanical longevity.",
